nl.tue.geometrycore.geometry

Interface GeometryConvertable<T extends BaseGeometry>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseGeometry, BezierCurve, Circle, CircularArc, CyclicGeometry, DCELDart, DCELVertex, GeometryCycle, GeometryGroup, GeometryString, HalfLine, Line, LineSegment, OrientedGeometry, ParameterizedCurve, Polygon, PolyLine, ReadItem, Rectangle, SimpleEdge, SimpleVertex, Vector

    public interface GeometryConvertable<T extends BaseGeometry>
    This interface implements a simple conversion-to-BaseGeometry to convert any object into a geometry representation. This is mostly used to allow generic functions for writing and drawing geometries, without requiring said objects to inherit from BaseGeometry.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      T toGeometry()
      Returns an object that inherits from BaseGeometry that represents this object.
